         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>l. 6. Misprinted as <foreign xml:lang="grc">εὐπε</foreign>- in <title level="m">ALA</title>.</p>
            <p>l. 10. Draft as given, but the mason only cut <foreign xml:lang="grc">ΚΥΙΕ</foreign>.</p>
            <p>l. 12. Draft as given, but the mason cut <foreign xml:lang="grc">Υ<space extent="1" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/>ΤΗΣ</foreign>.</p>
